size - -1/0/+1:              size           -55/0/+30
exp bonus:                   exp            +3 per 1% (max 25%)
stat bonus - +5%/10/15/20:   str, dex etc.  +15/+30/+60/+100
stat penalty - -5%/10/15/20: str, dex etc.  -15/-30/-60/-90
